    <h2> Poetry definitions</h2>
    
    <ol>
    	<li> The art of rhythmical composition, written or spoken, for exciting pleasure by beautiful, imaginative, or elevated thoughts. </li>
    	<li> Literary work in metrical form; verse.</li>
        <li> Prose with poetic qualities. </li>
    </ol>

